MBOMBELA &#8211; Builders Warehouse hosted its annual outdoor trade event on November 24, to thank contractors and clients for their continuous support over the past year. The Grove branch has been around for the last 10 years, and this was its ninth trade event.Finger foods, pastries and biltong were served with drinks. Staff members manned a boerewors braai.A local singer, Anton, entertained the guests.&#8220;We would like to thank everybody who supports us, and we would like everyone to know that we appreciate each and every staff member&#8217;s input to make this evening a success,&#8221; said manager, Ms Adele Potgieter.Also see: Medical aid shatters local dancer&#8217;s dream